{
  "texts": [
    "It also has a 384 core GPU with 48 tensor cores that makes it ideal for heavy video processing.",
    "This hardware is similar to that found as the companion boards on many commercial drones.",
    "We chose this development kit because it is equipped with the TrustZone and has an open and programmable secure world.",
    "We configured the secure world to run the Trusty TEE [52], which allows for easy development of trusted applications.",
    "The normal world runs Linux for Tegra (L4T) [58], which consists of the Linux kernel 4.9, a bootloader, and supporting drivers."
  ]
}